---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/case-study.css';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<BaseLayout title={`quiet instruments -- ${site.title}`} doodle={false} caseStudy="quiet instruments">

<header class="page-header">
  <div class="content">
    <h1 class="cs-title">quiet instruments</h1>
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <section class="cs-section">
    <div class="content">
      <p class="body-text">Most measurement tools announce themselves. They beep, they flash, they demand calibration. I wanted to build something that just listened. Quiet instruments is a collection of small programs that sit in the background and record things nobody asked them to: how long a window stays open, how many times a cursor reverses direction, the interval between saves.</p>
      <p class="body-text" style="margin-top: var(--sp-snug)">None of this data means anything on its own. But after a few weeks, patterns emerge that you can feel but couldn't name. The distance between intention and action has a shape. These instruments draw it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cs-section">
    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="cs-h2">what it does</h2>
      <p class="body-text">Run <code>qi start</code> and forget about it. It watches your working session and writes a daily log -- plain text, no database, nothing phoning home. After seven days you can run <code>qi reflect</code> and it generates a one-page summary of your rhythms. When you started. When you paused. Where you hesitated. The report is yours and it never leaves your machine.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cs-section">
    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="cs-h2">links</h2>
      <ul class="project-links">
        <li class="project-link-item">
          <span class="project-link-label">repo</span>
          <a href="https://github.com/yourname/project" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="project-link">github.com/adakosmik/quiet-instruments</a>
        </li>
        <li class="project-link-item">
          <span class="project-link-label">npm</span>
          <a href="https://example.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="project-link">npmjs.com/package/quiet-instruments</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer class="cs-footer">
  <div class="cs-wrap">
    <a href="/" class="cs-back">← back to work</a>
    <div class="cs-footer-brand">
      <span>{site.footer}</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

</BaseLayout>
